    <name>Compose Wrapper</name>
    <vendor>Mehrdad</vendor>

    <depends>com.intellij.modules.platform</depends>
    <depends>org.jetbrains.kotlin</depends>

    <description><![CDATA[
<p><b>Turbocharge your Jetpack Compose workflow!</b></p>

    <p>Quickly wrap your Composables with <code>Row</code>, <code>Column</code>, <code>Box</code>, or <code>Lazy</code> layouts using a single shortcut.</p>
