      <img src="https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/11981337/528299503-69252140-feb4-4186-ac80-4754b3e5c657.gif?jwt=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..3_J6xjg7ATvIKScW3ZmaE8kHXomJyomguijY1ir8B04">
    </p>
    <h3>‚ö° Key Features:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><b>Instant Wrap:</b> Press <i>Alt + Enter</i> to wrap code in seconds.</li>
        <li><b>Smart Lazy Layouts:</b> Automatically adds <code>item { }</code> blocks.</li>
        <li><b>Zero Config:</b> Auto-adds imports and reformats your code.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>ü§ù Open Source & Support:</h3>
